    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s ready for a brand-new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, so you're getting a great vehicle that's ready to hit the road. Come say hi and take it for a spin; I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
