    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface wear expected from a car that has been driven with care. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or odors, and every electronic feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has benefited from a strict adherence to its manufacturer-recommended service schedule, including a recent comprehensive inspection, fresh fluid service, and brake pad replacement. It starts reliably, idles smoothly, and provides a confident, quiet ride on the highway. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been loved by its previous owner. Includes a full set of service records and two original key fobs.",
      "price": 32500.0,
